	<string>Life OS uses the camera to scan barcodes on packaged food and to take meal photos for AI macro estimation.</string>
	<key>NSHealthShareUsageDescription</key>
	<string>Life OS reads your activity, heart rate, sleep, and body data from Apple Health to assemble your daily readiness picture.</string>
	<key>NSHealthUpdateUsageDescription</key>
	<string>Life OS writes weight, water, and mindful sessions you log here back to Apple Health so the rest of your apps stay in sync.</string>
	<key>NSMicrophoneUsageDescription</key>
	<string>Life OS records a short voice clip describing a meal so Gemini can estimate calories and macros.</string>
	<key>NSPhotoLibraryUsageDescription</key>
	<string>Life OS can analyze a meal photo from your library to estimate calories and macros.</string>
	<key>NSSupportsLiveActivities</key>
